32:09.830 --> 32:12.100
- Check out the floor, brand new floor.

32:12.100 --> 32:14.360
- [Marta] Yeah, so nice.

32:14.360 --> 32:16.463
- Look at the space over
there now with the bar.

32:16.463 --> 32:18.150
- [Marta] It's so nice.

32:18.150 --> 32:19.710
- [Melody] It's like out of a magazine.

32:19.710 --> 32:21.620
- This is what it's like during the day.

32:21.620 --> 32:22.605
Can you imagine what it's
going to be like at night?

32:22.605 --> 32:23.730
- [Melody] Oh, my goodness, you're right.

32:23.730 --> 32:25.447
- With the candles lit
on the table flickering.

32:25.447 --> 32:27.120
- This is what we've needed.

32:27.120 --> 32:28.709
I mean, we need guidance.

32:28.709 --> 32:31.180
We've just been spinning
our tyres for so long.

32:31.180 --> 32:32.609
- Right, and you happy?

32:32.609 --> 32:33.442
- [Marta] I'm happy.

32:33.442 --> 32:34.570
- Good, I'm glad you're happy.

32:34.570 --> 32:36.420
- I'm probably the most excited I've been

32:36.420 --> 32:39.890
