and grandbabies were born.

32:39.890 --> 32:41.989
I'm literally that excited.

32:41.989 --> 32:43.097
- [Jimmy] It's beautiful.
- [Marta] Oh, so beautiful.

32:43.097 --> 32:44.735
- Thank you so much.

32:44.735 --> 32:46.915
- You're welcome.

32:46.915 --> 32:50.082
(lively upbeat music)

32:52.840 --> 32:55.950
Now, let's talk food.

