34:47.560 --> 34:48.960
- Yeah, it's pretty.

34:48.960 --> 34:51.370
- While the castle has done
many events in the past

34:51.370 --> 34:54.210
I'm hoping this wedding
not only raises the bar,

34:54.210 --> 34:58.100
but puts it on the map
as a destinational spot.

34:58.100 --> 34:59.766
Gents, how are you? You
look great, by the way.

34:59.766 --> 35:01.510
- [Boy] Thank you.
- Ah, so smart.

35:01.510 --> 35:03.430
All good? You look smart as well.

35:03.430 --> 35:04.263
Where's Eric?

35:04.263 --> 35:05.096
- [Jimmy] He's already out there.

35:05.096 --> 35:06.923
- [Gordon] How are we looking?
